    public class SymbolTableVisitor
extends FEReplacer
    Front-end visitor pass that maintains a symbol table. Other passes that need symbol table information can extend this. The protected symtab member has the prevailing symbol table as each node is visited.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    David Maze <dmaze@cag.lcs.mit.edu>
